{"data":[{"date":"08:13 26/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 26/07: T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Martial g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/22/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-2607-tuong-lai-martial-gan-nhu-da-duoc-xac-dinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 26/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Martial g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 2607 T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 2607 T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-2607-Tuong-lai-Martial-duoc-xac-dinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial s\u1eafp r\u1eddi M.U v\u00ec m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eadu con trai s\u1eafp sinh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u01b0u ti\u00ean Chelsea h\u01a1n l\u00e0 M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio \u01b0u ti\u00ean Chelsea h\u01a1n l\u00e0 M.U trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Lazio. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Unai Emery tin Ozil s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd</h2>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, song HLV Unai Emery tin r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chris Smalling mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sau khi b\u1ecb b\u1ecf r\u01a1i \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chris-smalling-muon-chung-to-kha-nang-sau-khi-bi-bo-roi-o-world-cup-2018-172-192044.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/23/chris-smalling-muon-chung-to-kha-nang-sau-khi-bi-bo-roi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chris-smalling-muon-chung-to-kha-nang-sau-khi-bi-bo-roi-o-world-cup-2018-172-192044.html\">Chris Smalling mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sau khi b\u1ecb b\u1ecf r\u01a1i \u1edf World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nChris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Harry Maguire ho\u1eb7c Toby Alderweireld, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Manchester Evening News \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/Chelsea-ban-Alvaro-Morata-neu-nhan-duoc-58-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Morata v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gianluca Di Marzio ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Hi\u1ec7n AC Milan v\u00e0 Juventus \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>John Stones k\u1ecbp \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">John Stones t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Man City s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng hot Golovin t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Chelsea h\u1ecfi mua Rugani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chi dam mua Rugani\" title=\"Arsenal chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Rugani\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Chelsea-mua-Daniele-Rugani-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua mua Rugani</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Daniele Rugani, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Davide Torchia c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-chelsea-chi-45-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-juventus-172-192036.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/17/thuc-hu-vu-chelsea-chi-45-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-chelsea-chi-45-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-juventus-172-192036.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Chelsea chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Juventus</span><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Daniele Rugani, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Davide Torchia c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4649","checkdouble":"192049"},{"date":"07:44 26/07","title":"MU b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/18/mu-ban-marcos-rojo-de-dua-ve-trung-ve-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Harry Maguire ho\u1eb7c Toby Alderweireld, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Manchester Evening News \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 B\u00e1n Rojo mua Maguire ho\u1eb7c Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 B\u00e1n Rojo mua Maguire ho\u1eb7c Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/mu-ban-marcos-rojo-de-dua-ve-trung-ve-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 l\u00fac n\u00e0y b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Eric Bailly l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mouirnho \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, Rojo ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Smalling, Jones v\u00e0 Lindelof cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng dai d\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 mua trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Manchester Evening News \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf mu\u1ed1n\u00a0thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb 12 \u0111\u1ebfn 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U nh\u1eafm Maguire ho\u1eb7c Alderweireld n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng tin MU mua Toby Alderweireld \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u, song Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 b\u1edfi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Tottenham y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Theo Mirror, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alderweireld\" title=\"Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-2107.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alderweireld l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-tottenham-va-mu-trao-doi-bom-tan-172-191994.html\" target=\"_blank\"> M.U \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Alderweireld </span>c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00ean. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 Spurs c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi th\u00ec Martial v\u00e0 Alderweireld c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Toby Alderweireld, M.U s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester City. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d nh\u1ea3 Maguire, M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t khao m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4648","checkdouble":"192041"},{"date":"07:55 26/07","title":"Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb Milan \"ch\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/arsenal-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-bi-milan-chat-dau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trang ch\u1ee7 CLB th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o b\u00e1c b\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ivan Gazidis v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal m\u1ea5t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1ec1 tay Milan?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ivan Gazidis \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ean th\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea7ng Emirates t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2008 nay v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng. Th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u1ea5y l\u00ean v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng doanh nh\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nam Phi s\u1ebd chia tay Arsenal trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau c\u1ea3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 g\u1eafn b\u00f3.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">CLB \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Milan, \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Trung Qu\u1ed1c. \u00d4ng ch\u1ee7 c\u0169 Li Yonghong tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1n kho\u1ea3n n\u1ee3 cho t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Elliott Management gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u0110\u0110H Ivan Gazidis \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u0110\u0110H Ivan Gazidis \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/arsenal-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-bi-milan-chat-dau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>G\u0110\u0110H Ivan Gazidis \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ea1i gia r\u1edfm \u0111\u1eddi g\u1ed1c Hoa kia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i vay \u0111\u1ebfn 341 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi l\u00e3i su\u1ea5t 11,5% t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Elliott Management \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i Milan t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u1edbng \u00dd Silvio Berlusconi trong n\u0103m 2016. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Elliott Management \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Paolo Scaroni l\u00ean l\u00e0m t\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Gazidis ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Emirates</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed9c thay m\u00e1u ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Milan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Leonardo, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 v\u00e0 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Rossoneri nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i m\u1eddi l\u1ea1i n\u1ed1t Umberto Gandini l\u00e0m gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh sau th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Arseanal v\u1ec1 Ivan Gazidis.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trang ch\u1ee7 CLB th\u00e0nh London d\u1eabn l\u1eddi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Chips Keswick: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u00fd th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xoay quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ivan Gazidis, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng \u1ea5y nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng khi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i xin nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u1edbi n\u00e0o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f4ng khai chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 n\u00f3. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n cam k\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Arsenal, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang c\u00f9ng t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u1edf Singapore \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/unai-emery-cong-thuc-monchi-trong-giac-mo-tai-cau-truc-cua-arsenal-172-187023.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/25/unai-emery-cong-thuc-monchi-trong-giac-mo-tai-cau-truc-cua-arsenal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/unai-emery-cong-thuc-monchi-trong-giac-mo-tai-cau-truc-cua-arsenal-172-187023.html\">Unai Emery: C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c Monchi trong gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u00e1i c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac c\u1ee7a Arsenal</span><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i sao l\u00e0 Unai Emery?  Nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi th\u1ebf khi bi\u1ebft t\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf nhi\u1ec7m gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Arsenal. Nh\u01b0ng Unai Emery l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t trong b\u00e0i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4647","checkdouble":"192042"},{"date":"08:00 26/07","title":"Chris Smalling mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sau khi b\u1ecb b\u1ecf r\u01a1i \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/23/chris-smalling-muon-chung-to-kha-nang-sau-khi-bi-bo-roi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Smalling quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Chris Smalling l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/23/chris-smalling-muon-chung-to-kha-nang-sau-khi-bi-bo-roi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp Phil Jones ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Smalling, b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf ch\u1ed7 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i Jones d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Smalling xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBan \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n tham d\u1ef1. Sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1\u00a0g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ed5 \u00edch, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 du l\u1ecbch \u1edf Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat th\u00fa v\u1ecb \u1edf \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 sung s\u1ee9c, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho M.U. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Smalling kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n M.U mua trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, Mouirnho mu\u1ed1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/trung-ve-khung-dang-tren-duong-cap-ben-old-trafford-172-191829.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester </span>ho\u1eb7c Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, song Smalling kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling toa sang thuong xuyen o mua giai nay\" title=\"Smalling t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/19/smalling-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quen v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n h\u00e0ng n\u0103m, M.U lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho M.U, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1eddi M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song t\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Old Trafford\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4646","checkdouble":"192044"},{"date":"08:28 26/07","title":"\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sao Juventus x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/chinh-thuc-cuu-sao-chelsea-tro-ve-anh-khoac-ao-tan-binh-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Rugani</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Chelsea ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap The Blues gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA, HLV Antonio Conte v\u1eabn b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Italia, Maurizio Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSarri \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. H\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Napoli l\u00e0 Jorginho l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng mang v\u1ec1 Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 59 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng Gonzalo Higuain v\u00e0 Daniele Rugani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Chelsea-quan-tam-Rugani-cua-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV\u00a0Sarri mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 c\u00e1c tr\u00f2 c\u0169</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHiguain t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbng Sarri m\u00f9a 2015/16, \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh cao s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi 38 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 42 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. C\u00f2n Rugani, ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o Empoli t\u1eebng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i CLB giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u0103m 2013 t\u1edbi 2015.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRugani \u0111ang c\u00f9ng Juventus tham d\u1ef1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh, Davide Torchia m\u1edbi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Chelsea d\u00f9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Rugani\" title=\"hau ve Rugani\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/chinh-thuc-cuu-sao-chelsea-tro-ve-anh-khoac-ao-tan-binh-premier-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cChelsea quan t\u00e2m Rugani l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eadt\u201d, Torchia n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Radio Sportiva. \u201cNgo\u00e0i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n khi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Juventus. Nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Gonzalo Higuain l\u00e0 ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t. M\u1ed7i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 chi ph\u00ed kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c nhau.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i cho Juventus nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ee3i kh\u00e1c nhau. C\u00f2n Rugani, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 Juventus. Rugani v\u1eabn \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb song c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eadp trung cao nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-chelsea-chi-45-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-juventus-172-192036.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Chelsea chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-tri-gia-100-trieu-euro-cua-mu-muon-gia-nhap-chelsea-172-192026.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ee7a MU mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-dat-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-courtois-180-192010.html\">N\u00f3ng: Sao Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-mua-kante-neu-mat-pjanic-vao-tay-man-city-172-191995.html\">V\u00ec Man City, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Kante v\u00e0o tay Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-bailey-thay-willian-172-191982.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean Chelsea s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Willian cho M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4645","checkdouble":"192045"},{"date":"08:29 26/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Anh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o t\u00e2n binh Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/26/Chinh-thuc-Tien-dao-Andre-Schurrle-gia-nhap-Fulham-tu-Dortmund-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fulham ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 28 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c Andre Schurrle t\u1eeb Dortmund theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n hai n\u0103m.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh Premier League 2018/19 \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u0103n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh Wolverhampton, Fulham c\u0169ng \u0111ang g\u00e2y n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Jean Michael Seri \u2013 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Arsenal, Chelsea hay Barcelona theo \u0111u\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Andre Schurrle gia nh\u1eadp Fulham t\u1eeb Dortmund h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Andre Schurrle gia nh\u1eadp Fulham t\u1eeb Dortmund h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Chinh-thuc-Tien-dao-Andre-Schurrle-gia-nhap-Fulham-tu-Dortmund-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Andre Schurrle gia nh\u1eadp Fulham t\u1eeb Dortmund theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong hai n\u0103m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, CLB T\u00e2y London m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng kh\u00e1c, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup b\u1ed1n n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Andre Schurrle ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Fulham t\u1eeb Dortmund theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n hai n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ed1n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng l\u1ea1 g\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh khi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1eeb 2013-2015 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB T\u00e2y London kh\u00e1c. Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League trong n\u0103m 2015.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, Schurrle ra \u0111i h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o nh\u1eefng Wolfsburg r\u1ed3i Dortmund nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn Fulham \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 14 quen thu\u1ed9c \u1edf Craven Cottage, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cFulham l\u00e0 CLB \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 t\u00f4i, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Fulham. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n h\u1eefu \u00edch n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-hang-hot-ligue-1-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191053.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/chinh-thuc-hang-hot-ligue-1-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-hang-hot-ligue-1-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191053.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: H\u00e0ng hot Ligue 1 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span><br>\r\nJean Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fulham, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi NHM b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4644","checkdouble":"192047"},{"date":"21:52 25/07","title":"B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ph\u01a1i b\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/bui-tien-dung-phoi-bay-nhieu-van-de-sau-tran-thua-cua-flc-thanh-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng sau tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 SLNA chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/7.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng m\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed7i trong tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u00fap QG gi\u1eefa FLC Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA, tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng khi anh li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 18 v\u00e0 22, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh x\u1ee9 Thanh \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng sau nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh Jemie Dwayne v\u00e0 Olaha\u00a0. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 87, Jemie Dwayne m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap SLNA gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-2 chung cu\u1ed9c.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00f3a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00f3a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/photo1532520078312-15325200783121187103518.jpg\" /></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9\u00a0nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u00edt d\u1ea7n \u0111i. Trong khi v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cm\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018 b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c b\u00e0n thua m\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb l\u1ed7i c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o 3 b\u00e0n thua m\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1997 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc c\u00e1c l\u1ed7i ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, ra v\u00e0o thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee3p l\u00ed v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. \u1ede b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n, ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng bay v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng ra \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf b\u00e0n thua cu\u1ed1i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m b\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng khi\u1ebfn Jermie Lynch\u00a0c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec7m l\u00f2ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u00ecn \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/that-thu-tren-san-nha-thay-cua-bui-tien-dung-noi-gi-168-192021.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/that-thu-tren-san-nha-thay-cua-bui-tien-dung-noi-gi.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/that-thu-tren-san-nha-thay-cua-bui-tien-dung-noi-gi-168-192021.html\">Th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<b><span style=\"font-size: 17pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; color: rgb(76, 73, 71); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4643","checkdouble":"192028"},{"date":"22:01 25/07","title":"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 gi\u1eefa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-giai-thich-su-ky-gio-giua-ha-noi-va-binh-duong.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u00f3 l\u00fac b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 1-3 nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam khi t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Th\u00e0nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 Oseni, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tho\u00e1t thua v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 3-3.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/IMG_0887.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 khi\u1ebfn B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng lu\u00f4n g\u00e2y ra kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: &quot;Do s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 gi\u1eefa hai c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ea5t m\u00e1u l\u1eeda v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ganh \u0111ua. B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t&quot;.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng con ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i c\u1ea7m nh\u1ecbp t\u1ed1t, V\u0103n V\u0169 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u00f2n Ti\u1ebfn Linh l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed1t. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n qua h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, t\u1eeb d\u01b0\u1edbi ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng l\u00ean th\u00ec H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1eaft, c\u00f2n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1ed1t \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong b\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i U23 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem yeu lon nhat cua Do Hung Dung la luon lam nen cho nguoi khac.\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/IMG_0996.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&quot;V\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i th\u00ec H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu, lu\u00f4n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u cho \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn&quot; - V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;T\u01b0 duy chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u1ee7a D\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha D\u0169ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngay nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam cho r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9i chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018 cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay v\u1eabn \u0111ang th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 90% m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 gi\u1eefa B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 17h00 ng\u00e0y 5/9.<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/gay-kho-khan-cho-ha-noi-hlv-tran-minh-chien-giau-bai-291-192025.html\">G\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn gi\u1ea5u b\u00e0i cho tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/ha-noi-vs-binh-duong-ban-ket-cup-quoc-gia-viet-nam-2018-372-191996.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 3-3 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (KT): L\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tho\u00e1t thua, CLB Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-20-vleague-su-vo-doi-cua-ha-noi-168-191828.html\">Sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League: S\u1ef1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-ha-noi-tuyen-bo-tu-tin-sau-tran-thang-thanh-hoa-168-191784.html\">HLV H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1ef1 tin sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Thanh H\u00f3a</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nguoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-phai-thua-nhan-mot-su-that-168-191753.html\">Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/thanh-hoa-vs-ha-noi-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191730.html\">Thanh H\u00f3a 2-3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4642","checkdouble":"192030"},{"date":"23:16 25/07","title":"Chuy\u00ean gia lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 V\u0169 M\u1ea1nh H\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23+3, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u00ean gia lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u00ean gia lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ee9c Huy v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 V\u0169 M\u1ea1nh H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn: &ldquo;Theo t\u00f4i, nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i khi\u1ebfn cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u01b0\u1edbc trong khu v\u1ef1c h\u1ecd t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f4i khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng mang l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i. H\u1ecd t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng \u0111i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd h\u01a1n, t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u0129 h\u01a1n, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i hay l\u00e0 coi th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa. N\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang ta gi\u1edd \u1edf m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta th\u00ec c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t r\u00f5. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb ch\u00fang ta, c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd m\u00e0 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft th\u00ec b\u00e2y gi\u1edd h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3 r\u1ed3i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang ta nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng, khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u1edb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u00c1 qu\u00e2n Ch\u00e2u \u00c1&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout-168-192005.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout-168-192005.html\">ASIAD 2018: Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, kh\u00f3 th\u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out</span><br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a 26 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung, v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung cao. B\u1ea5t k\u00ec sai l\u1ea7m n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1. B\u1edfi th\u1ebf t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao nh\u01b0 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u1edf U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 th\u00ec r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cao nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u1eefa th\u00ec t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc, qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nay c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch cho Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ngang h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea5u di\u1ebfm n\u1eefa. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3&rdquo;, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Th\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac cu\u1ed9c chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eed l\u1eeda quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo ki\u1ec3m tra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4641","checkdouble":"192032"},{"date":"23:35 25/07","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u sao U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-yeu-cau-sao-u23-viet-nam-giam-can.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m PVF, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ra ch\u1ec9 th\u1ecb y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ph\u1ea3i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c r\u01b0\u1edbn.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-yeu-cau-Ha-Duc-Chinh-giam-can-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o d\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. \u1ea2nh: Webthethao</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 25/7, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra s\u00e2n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. \u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, do ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 n\u00ean HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nh\u00f3m c\u1ef1 li ng\u1eafn v\u1edbi tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh nhanh ch\u00f3ng gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd m\u1eb7c \u00e1o m\u01b0a l\u00f3t ph\u00eda trong khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ee1 th\u1eeba nh\u1eb1m gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 c\u00e2n theo nh\u01b0 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 th\u1ea7y Park y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng c\u00e2n trong th\u1ea5y so v\u1edbi h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha b\u1ee9t ph\u00e1 qu\u00e3ng ng\u1eafn t\u1ed1t. Do v\u1eady, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y Park r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp cho ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Indonesia v\u00e0o trung tu\u1ea7n th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192032.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192032.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 V\u0169 M\u1ea1nh H\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout-168-192005.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout-168-192005.html\">ASIAD 2018: Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, kh\u00f3 th\u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out</span><br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a 26 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4640","checkdouble":"192033"},{"date":"23:56 25/07","title":"Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/quang-hai-doi-mua-chien-dau-truoc-ngay-hoi-quan-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a c\u00f9ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i k\u1ecbch chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.\r\n</h2><div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\