 N\u1ed9i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Binh Duong choi tot hon khi da co luc dan truoc 3-1 nho cong cua Dinh Hoang Max va To Van Vu (cu dup).\" title=\"B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-1 nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110inh Ho\u00e0ng Max v\u00e0 T\u00f4 V\u0103n V\u0169 (c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap).\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/IMG_1024.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-1 nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110inh Ho\u00e0ng Max v\u00e0 T\u00f4 V\u0103n V\u0169 (c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap).</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu thanh Tan Truong cung co mot ngay thi dau tot khi nhieu lan giai nguy cho Binh Duong.\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh T\u1ea5n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t khi nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i nguy cho B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/IMG_1035.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh T\u1ea5n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t khi nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i nguy cho B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du vay, nhung no luc trong thoi gian cuoi tran giup Ha Noi co duoc tran hoa 3-3.\" title=\"D\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn gi\u00fap H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/IMG_1055.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>D\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn gi\u00fap H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau tran dau, Quang Hai duoc cac fan nhi vay quanh xin chu ky va chup anh chung.\" title=\"Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c fan nh\u00ed v\u00e2y quanh xin ch\u1eef k\u00fd v\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh chung.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/IMG_1062.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c fan nh\u00ed v\u00e2y quanh xin ch\u1eef k\u00fd v\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh chung.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Quang H\u1ea3i:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-quang-nam-vs-ha-noi-17h00-ngay-96-vleague-2018-372-188119.html\">Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 0-1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vuot-sieu-pham-cua-cong-phuong-quang-hai-dan-dau-danh-sach-ban-thang-dep-vong-11-168-187799.html\">T\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m C\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng tuy\u1ebft, Quang H\u1ea3i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00f2ng 11</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-ha-noi-vs-khanh-hoa-19h00-ngay-36-vleague-2018-372-187654.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 4-0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a (KT): Quang H\u1ea3i s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, \u0111\u1ed9c c\u00f4 c\u1ea7u b\u1ea1i l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng to</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/quang-hai-chan-thuong-ha-noi-gap-kho-truoc-chuyen-lam-khach-slna-291-187231.html\">Quang H\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch SLNA</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/quang-hai-tien-dung-hai-con-nguoi-mot-so-phan-167-187066.html\">Quang H\u1ea3i &ndash; Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng: Hai con ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-khien-quang-hai-sa-sut-tai-vleague-2018-291-187014.html\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Quang H\u1ea3i sa s\u00fat t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4639","checkdouble":"192034"},{"date":"05:24 26/07","title":"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: H\u00e0ng hot Golovin t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/26/xac-nhan-hang-hot-golovin-tim-duoc-ben-do-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Monaco \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Golovin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CSKA Moscow, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Chelsea, Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Chelsea, Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/xac-nhan-hang-hot-golovin-tim-duoc-ben-do-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Golovin c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Monaco v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Golovin c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Nga. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga v\u00e0o t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-viec-cska-dong-y-ban-golovin-cho-chelsea-172-191470.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Golovin</span>, Juventus, M.U v\u00e0 Arsenal l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga, song Monaco m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMonaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Monaco, anh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 6.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Golovin c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Monaco.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Golovin ch\u1ecdn Monaco thay v\u00ec Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c thay v\u00ec Chelsea ho\u1eb7c Juventus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Golovin la cau thu choi hay nhat ben phia Nga khi ghi 1 ban va kien tao 2 ban khac\" title=\"Golovin l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Nga khi ghi 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 2 b\u00e0n kh\u00e1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/thuc-hu-viec-cska-dong-y-ban-golovin-cho-chelsea.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMonaco v\u00e0 CSKA \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Golovin. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Ngo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec Juventus c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, song \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec Golovin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Monaco, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a CLB ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, \u1edf Monaco kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Golovin c\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Chelsea. T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf Stamford Bridge, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Monaco\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4638","checkdouble":"192035"},{"date":"20:07 25/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 25/7: M.U ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-256-mu-tiep-can-nha-a-quan-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018, HLV Conte s\u1eafp t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t, Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chia tay hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 25/6</h2><br>\r\n<h2>M.U ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Rebic<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Sport Bild\u00a0ti\u1ebfng \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 chuy\u1ec7n CLB Man United \u0111ang h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ante Rebic t\u1eeb CLB Eintracht Frankfurt. Rebic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i. C\u0169ng theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Rebic, M.U s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 66 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 257 MU ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 257 MU ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-256-mu-tiep-can-nha-a-quan-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Rebic\u00a0\u00a0t\u1eeb CLB Eintracht Frankfurt</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Chelsea v\u00e0 Liverpool c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n M.U<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea, Liverpool hay k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n M.U trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \u201cT\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng HLV n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 6 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. H\u00e3y xem Chelsea v\u00e0 Liverpool. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e2u thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 Arsenal c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba, Romelu Lukaku, Marcus Rashford, Jesse Lingard, Marouane Fellaini, Ashley Young v\u00e0 Phil Jones, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba v\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<h2>HLV Conte s\u1eafp t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Serie A<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi HLV Conte b\u1ecb CLB Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u00ecnh b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1edd Corriere dello Sport \u0111\u01b0a tin Antonio Conte l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Milan trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5n h\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Conte, Milan c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Arsenal l\u00e0 \u00f4ng\u00a0Ivan Gazidis.</p>\r\n<h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Scholes lo M.U ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1eafng tay<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Man Utd tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford Paul Scholes nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh M.U kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. N\u1ebfu m\u00f9a n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u th\u00ec \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm \u1edf Champions League b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Sevilla. H\u1ecd thua cu\u1ed9c \u1edf chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap FA. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec c\u1ea3\u201d, Paul Scholes n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n<h2>Barca s\u1eafp chia tay hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, CLB Barcelona nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd chia tay hai g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lucas Digne v\u00e0 Yerry Mina.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Digne kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Jordi Alba. Anh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Everton trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 19 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Yerry Mina c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo s\u00e1t sau k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Colombia. Trung v\u1ec7 ghi ba b\u00e0n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 qua c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 Lyon l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>HLV Arsenal \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Ozil sau scandal b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c do b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c, t\u00e2n HLV Arsenal, Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean cho c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Mesut \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng b\u1edfi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf Arsenal. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh cho m\u1ed7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \", HLV Unai Emery cho hay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ozil \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, \u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \"T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>Mourinho mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 tr\u00f2 c\u0169 William</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mundo Deportivo, Mourinho s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a Willian v\u1ec1 Chelsea t\u1eeb Shakhtar Donetsk h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 8/2013. \u00d4ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh v\u00e0 n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-sang-257-cristiano-ronaldo-khoe-hon-ca-cau-thu-20-tuoi-184-191962.html\" target=\"_blank\">Xem th\u00eam: \u0110I\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 25/7: Cho\u00e1ng v\u1ec1 b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m \u00a0tra y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4637","checkdouble":"192016"}]}